<section class="section section--compact" id="w2q-credentials">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Certified by Intuit</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor credentials</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">Leaving Wave for QuickBooks means building the destination file correctly &mdash; the right chart of accounts, lists, and structure that Wave never asked you to think about. Every TechBrot operator holds active Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor credentials across the full QuickBooks stack, plus the Intuit Certified Bookkeeping Professional credential. Verification available on request.</p>
